---
title: Garlic Prawn & Chorizo Tacos with Cucumber, Cos Salad & Chipotle Aioli
description: Jazz up taco night by kicking things off with a layer of chipotle aioli. We’re keeping the groove alive by busting out our best move - chorizo and garlicky prawns. Let your tastebuds dance the night away.
